We would like to enhance the BitBucket Jenkins Integration [1]. Specifically we want to handle active and merged branches different. Unfortunate the REST API does not provide any information on whether a branch is active or merged. Therefore we ask you to expose this information through any REST API call. e.g. add an additional &#x27;active&#x27; field in the response of

{{GET [https://bitbucket.org/api/1.0/repositories/myuser/myrepo/branches}}

{code}
{
  "feature/BB": {
    "node": "7edb46d80563",
    "files": [
      {
        "type": "modified",
        "file": "contributors.txt"
      }
    ],
