When a user tries to make changes on a file in their repo and commit online from the Bitbucket UI, they will hit an error message &#x27;We had trouble committing your changes.&#x27;

!969865630-Screen%20Shot%202016-09-09%20at%209.24.49%20PM.png|thumbnail!

Trying to edit a file on Bitbucket, clicking &#x27;View Diff&#x27; will fail as well with the error &#x27;We had trouble generating your preview.&#x27;

!1909838507-Screen%20Shot%202016-09-09%20at%209.22.57%20PM.png|thumbnail!

Workaround: Edit the files locally, and then push up the changes to the remote repo.

